snippet.title: "優しさの記憶" KR Vocal&Piano (Lyrics Subtilte) / Blue Archive Final Chapter ED OST 'Memories of Kindness'
snippet.description:
Blue Archive - Final Chapter ED "優しさの記憶(Memories of Kindness)" Piano Performance


* This is a KR vocal version of a recently work.
* Piano only version: https://youtu.be/cC9w14YGEeQ


Today's performance is the ending theme "優しさの記憶" of the final chapter of the Blue Archive.

With this, the first act of the Blue Archive has really come down haha
It's really impressive... Now that the animation comes out, it's really... T_T

Thank you always to the production crew who have worked so hard!!
Thank you for listening.
---------------------------------------------------
Twitch : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
Discord : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
---------------------------------------------------
Blue Archive Main Title OST 「Constant Moderato」 Piano Play : https://youtu.be/qOGJzArDknQ
Blue Archive Memorial BGM 「Midnight Trip」 Piano Play : https://youtu.be/VLaDJCDIA8Q
Blue Archive 1st Anniversary PV OST(Luminous Memory) Piano Play : https://youtu.be/1xhW91bbFS8
[1st Anniversary] Blue Archive 「Target For Love」 Piano & Guitar Ver. : https://youtu.be/fC7HWUYQLdQ
---------------------------------------------------
템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
---------------------------------------------------
